# Balakhani, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Balakhani (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Balakhansky Selsoviet, Untsukulsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 11 streets.
Geography
Balakhani is located 28&nbsp;km south of Shamilkala (the district's administrative centre) by road. Irganay is the nearest rural locality.
